    "It is a technique to assist ChatGPT in remembering or focusing on particular actions, ideas, or behaviors when it is asked to generate inappropriate content [285].",
    "One potential simple defense strategy is to identify the presence of \"red-flagged\" keywords [276] which strictly violates the usage policies of the LLM vendors, e.g., OpenAI [54].",
    "Recently, Zhang et al.",
    "proposed a goal prioritization technique that prioritizes generating harmless responses over helpful ones at the inference phase [320].",
    "This technique can significantly reduce the success rate of jailbreaking attacks in ChatGPT and Llama-2."
